README
======

This file provides explanations regarding the PyMorphogenesis project.

REQUIREMENTS
------------

This program has been tested with python 2.5. It requires PyQt4, NumPy,
SciPy and pyglet. It has been tested with PyQt4 4.4.4, NumPy 1.2.1,
SciPy 0.7.0 and Pyglet 1.1.2.

INSTALLATION
------------

Appart from the dependencies, no installation should be necessary.

USAGE
-----

Simply run

	python PyMorphogenesis.py

For additional usage information, you can run

	python PyMorphogenesis.py --help
